title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: New Vehicles
content:
Money Fronts introduces six new vehicles, including the Överflöd Suzume, a supercar that’s available early to GTA+ Members through June 25 and free for Members to claim at The Vinewood Car Club until July 16.

Bring the rustic vibes of Paleto Forest wherever you go with the Karin Woodlander SUV. Plus, there’s the super responsive Dewbauchee Rapid GT X sports car, the new Annis Hardy sedan, and more to come.
